            "content": "<div class=\"s-prose js-post-body\" itemprop=\"text\">\n<h1>Yes</h1>\n<p>For a memory access breakpoint<sup>1</sup>, just <code>right click</code> the desired address &gt; <code>Breakpoint</code> &gt; <code>Memory, on access</code>:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/5bTxG.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img alt=\"Code hwbp\" src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/5bTxG.png\"/></a></p>\n<p>The same applies to values in the hex dump:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/LW2vG.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img alt=\"Data hwbp\" src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/LW2vG.png\"/></a></p>\n<p>1: A breakpoint on <em>access</em> will break whenver the address is read, written or executed. An <em>execution</em> breakpoint will <em>never</em> break on read/write.</p>\n</div>",
